briefdescription.para: Registers the ScalarWrapper class template with pybind11, adding various operations and constructors.

detaileddescription.para: This function template registers the ScalarWrapper class in the given Python module with specified names for the class and its scalar type. It adds support for basic arithmetic operations, comparisons, and string representation.

parameterdescription.para: The type of the scalar value to be wrapped.
The pybind11 module where the class will be registered.
The name of the class in the Python module.
The cpp name of the scalar type in the Python module.
